# EM32 Watchdog driver configuration

config WDT_EM32
	bool "ELAN EM32 Watchdog driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ELAN_EM32_WDT_ENABLED
	help
	  Enable Watchdog driver for ELAN EM32 family microcontrollers.
	  
	  The EM32 Watchdog controller supports:
	  - 32-bit down counter with configurable timeout
	  - Reset generation on timeout
	  - Interrupt generation before reset (optional)
	  - Lock mechanism to prevent accidental configuration changes
	  - Feed operation to reset the counter
